article_id:1502,category_name:News,title_name:Announcing Gala Dragalia Remix!,image_path:,message:<div>Gala Dragalia Remix will start at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1597384800"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>What are Gala Dragalia and Gala Dragalia Remix?</div><div>・The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons will be boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5★ summon or 5★ featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">・The newly added 5★ adventurers Yukata Cassandra (flame) and Yukata Curran (light) will also appear in the next summon showcase.</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">・Adventurers added in past Gala Dragalia summon showcases may appear in this summon showcase as well. For information about which adventurers may appear, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Appearance Rates and check the Appearance Rates section.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia Remix event duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1597384800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1597643999"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the featured adventurers below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurers:</div><div>
